{"tid":631143,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳瀅自爆俄羅斯有艷遇 俄國羅密歐約睇北極光","createTime":"2018-04-16T08:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T08:49:45.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"91a188c98fd75d9061fd5ccc11ba4909fd6f46f9","tid":631143,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T08:12:49.000Z","msg":"陳瀅、雨僑和倪晨曦今日喺尖沙嘴出席品牌iBLUES發佈會，陳瀅上星期到俄羅斯拍攝旅遊節目時有艷遇，佢甜笑話：「話說嗰日去玩雪上電單車，返屋企途中，(佢)問可唔可以車我返屋企，因為佢太有型，所以我上咗車，之後佢仲問我想唔想一齊睇北極光，當時自己面都紅哂，話遲啲先講，但係嗰日之後就見唔到個男仔。」陳瀅指對方叫做羅密歐，還問她：「Do you want to be my Juliet？」雖然對方高大靚仔，可惜緣份未到。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180412/large/1523538392_906d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180412%2Flarge%2F1523538392_906d.jpg&h=c8393e06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d900bf4aff088aa6a8013c2812c851b081e7da1","tid":631143,"uid":19208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T08:14:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ee2179d9efec2c6f8b9a3b3978bdcd26362491","tid":631143,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T08:14:50.000Z","msg":"又做免費雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67da999a99bb070c3daa9049e26e3f6a5c36cc3","tid":631143,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T08:15:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 臭雞"},{"pid":"080c447445e3fcd5c60204d16587cc832e6b9375","tid":631143,"uid":1565,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T08:41:47.000Z","msg":"係咪都留句臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  厭唔撚厭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你老母比你老豆溝個陣<br />\n依架分享返出黎你老母都係臭雞啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma